$timescale 1ns $end
$comment
  JTAG (IEEE 1149.1) Pro decoder happy-path fixture.
  Sequence:
    1. Reset to TLR (5 TMS=1 cycles)
    2. IR = IDCODE (0x1, b0001)
    3. DR = 32-bit IDCODE 0x1234ABCD on TDO
    4. IR = BYPASS (0xF, b1111)
    5. DR = 8-bit BYPASS push (TDI 1011_0010, TDO 10101010)
    6. IR = SAMPLE/PRELOAD (0x2, b0010)
    7. DR = 8-bit scan with mixed TDI/TDO
  Regenerate via: dart run tool/generate_jtag_fixture.dart
$end
$scope module tb $end
$var wire 1 ! TCK $end
$var wire 1 @ TMS $end
$var wire 1 ^ TDI $end
$var wire 1 % TDO $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
$dumpvars
0!
0@
0^
0%
$end
